"{\"uid\": \"rnz.co.nz-news-olympics-2024-523891-olympics-2024-there-are-tough-jobs-in-tahiti-surf-forecasting-is-one\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"ByLincoln Feast, Reuters  The surf break at Teahupo'o.Photo:Getty Images / Ryan Pierse  Kevin Wallis might have just about the toughest job atthe Olympic surfing venue of Teahupo'o in Tahitithis week.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 200, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 17, \"end\": 24, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 4.705900620004929e-13, \"text\": \"Reuters\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As director of forecasting at Surfline.com, which partners with the Olympic surfing organisers, the American has to tell them what conditions will be like, days in advance and down to the last minute, to advise of the best times to run competition.\", \"from\": 202, \"to\": 450, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 302, \"end\": 310, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999972131061167, \"rank\": 2.3838387891172636e-06, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Doing that ona remote island in the South Pacificis mostly science, but there is some art too.\", \"from\": 452, \"to\": 546, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read more:  Wednesday brought home the challenges of making a call.\", \"from\": 548, \"to\": 615, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"With time running out to finish competition, organisers decided to send the women's round three out into a maelstrom of 4.5-metre stormy surf at one of the world's most dangerous waves.\", \"from\": 617, \"to\": 802, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They quickly changed their minds and cancelled competition for the day, leaving a nail-biting wait to wrap up the event and decide the medals.\", \"from\": 804, \"to\": 946, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is a 10-day window (for competition) and we have got four days to run all the way through the event,\\\" Wallis told Reuters.\", \"from\": 948, \"to\": 1077, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1069, \"end\": 1076, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 4.705900620004929e-13, \"text\": \"Reuters\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In a perfect world, you get four really great days of surf like we had on Monday morning, but that does not always happen.\", \"from\": 1079, \"to\": 1202, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have been super lucky so far.\", \"from\": 1204, \"to\": 1237, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We have had two and a half days of anywhere from good to unbelievably all-time good in the case of Monday morning.\", \"from\": 1238, \"to\": 1352, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So I would just look whether we get anything more like that the rest of the waiting period - probably not - but we have got a day and a half to finish.\", \"from\": 1354, \"to\": 1506, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We have got to try and find the best day and a half left in the waiting period.\\\"\", \"from\": 1507, \"to\": 1587, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Portugal's Yolanda Hopkins turns off the lip of a wave at Teahupo'o.Photo:AFP / Ben Thouard  Monday's waves were somewhat atypical, with a westerly swell that created thick slabs of water when they hit Teahupo'o's unique reef, providing spectacular viewing and challenging conditions even for the world's best surfers.\", \"from\": 1589, \"to\": 1907, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1589, \"end\": 1597, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Portugal\", \"score\": 0.9163366797526461, \"rank\": 0.07562939795551665, \"text\": \"Portugal\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Portugal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Portugal\"}, {\"begin\": 1600, \"end\": 1607, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Typhoon_Haiyan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6151663316042436e-14, \"text\": \"Yolanda\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Typhoon_Haiyan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Typhoon_Haiyan\"}, {\"begin\": 1608, \"end\": 1615, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bernard_Hopkins\", \"score\": 0.9997049067084701, \"rank\": 0.0002469575140228324, \"text\": \"Hopkins\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bernard_Hopkins\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bernard_Hopkins\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In this case, we had a low develop over near Fiji almost due west of Tahiti and then it kind of dived down to the south of Tahiti.\", \"from\": 1909, \"to\": 2040, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1955, \"end\": 1959, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fiji\", \"score\": 0.9999999999899956, \"rank\": 5.645118431566045e-12, \"text\": \"Fiji\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fiji\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fiji\"}, {\"begin\": 1979, \"end\": 1985, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"score\": 0.9999988407059744, \"rank\": 1.1592952482224872e-06, \"text\": \"Tahiti\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\"}, {\"begin\": 2033, \"end\": 2039, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"score\": 0.9999988407059744, \"rank\": 1.1592952482224872e-06, \"text\": \"Tahiti\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So it set up a very westerly swell to start with, which is not unprecedented, but not typical either.\\\"\", \"from\": 2041, \"to\": 2143, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The weather system also drove some interesting local winds.\", \"from\": 2145, \"to\": 2204, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"clocking around and doing all sorts of weird things\\\" due to the mountains and canyons behind the village, he said.\", \"from\": 2205, \"to\": 2320, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"As that storm moved all the way past and the front came through, winds shifted in the west, onshore, it's poured rain ...\", \"from\": 2322, \"to\": 2444, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It went from as good as it gets to about as bad as it gets in an hour.\\\"\", \"from\": 2445, \"to\": 2516, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"With the clock counting down to complete the event, Wallis is in hot demand from surfers, officials and media.\", \"from\": 2518, \"to\": 2628, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My popularity it wanes with how good the waves actually look.\", \"from\": 2630, \"to\": 2692, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But, yeah, everyone's obviously interested in what the waves were doing over the next few days.\", \"from\": 2693, \"to\": 2788, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So Monday's epic conditions maybe made him some friends?\", \"from\": 2790, \"to\": 2846, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I look back and it wasn't a perfect forecast by any means ... but, yeah, under promise, over deliver.\", \"from\": 2848, \"to\": 2950, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's always a good rule of thumb in forecasting.\\\"\", \"from\": 2951, \"to\": 3002, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And the verdict for the days ahead?\", \"from\": 3004, \"to\": 3039, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Thursday is looking decent with solid, overhead waves but maybe still a little jumbled, then small and, at best, only decent surf for the remainder of the waiting period.\", \"from\": 3040, \"to\": 3210, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A surfer himself - \\\"that's how I got into this racket\\\" - Wallis said during Tuesday's stormy weather he might go for a quick wave, but at a little river mouth break near the main reef.\", \"from\": 3212, \"to\": 3396, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Ah no ... Well, maybe the river mouth here.\", \"from\": 3398, \"to\": 3442, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But out at Teahupo'o - no way,\\\" he said laughing.\", \"from\": 3443, \"to\": 3492, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's terrifying out there right now.\\\"\", \"from\": 3494, \"to\": 3532, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"- Reuters  Copyright \\u00a92024,Radio New Zealand  Tahiti's Teahupo'o stole the show at the Olympic surfing with some of the most incredible waves on Earth.\", \"from\": 3534, \"to\": 3685, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As the Olympics get going in earnest this week, not everyone's attention is focused on host city Paris.\", \"from\": 3687, \"to\": 3790, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3784, \"end\": 3789, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999845386, \"rank\": 1.526474259306491e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Surf fans are heading to Tahiti, half a world away in French Polynesia.\", \"from\": 3791, \"to\": 3862, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3816, \"end\": 3822, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"score\": 0.9999988407059744, \"rank\": 1.1592952482224872e-06, \"text\": \"Tahiti\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\"}, {\"begin\": 3852, \"end\": 3861, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Polynesia\", \"score\": 0.9868324744408489, \"rank\": 0.013343222786215797, \"text\": \"Polynesia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Polynesia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Polynesia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"New Zealand surfer Billy Stairmand gave the Brazilian world champion a fright before being eliminated from the Olympics.\", \"from\": 3864, \"to\": 3984, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As French Polynesia's Olympic surfing competition begins at the weekend, it will be the only event to host athletes in a floating hotel.\", \"from\": 3986, \"to\": 4122, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3996, \"end\": 4005, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Polynesia\", \"score\": 0.9868324744408489, \"rank\": 0.013343222786215797, \"text\": \"Polynesia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Polynesia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Polynesia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When are the Olympics, how much do tickets cost and where can I watch?\", \"from\": 4124, \"to\": 4194, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We have got all the answers to these questions - and more - here.\", \"from\": 4195, \"to\": 4260, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"for ad-free news and current affairs  Olympics 2024 RSS  Follow RNZ News\", \"from\": 4262, \"to\": 4334, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4314, \"end\": 4317, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RSS\", \"score\": 0.9999942132925836, \"rank\": 5.7751229764610226e-06, \"text\": \"RSS\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RSS\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RSS\"}, {\"begin\": 4326, \"end\": 4329, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Radio_New_Zealand\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"RNZ\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Radio_New_Zealand\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Radio_New_Zealand\"}]}]}"